{"tid":477460,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"《01》引消息：北京定23條立法時間  明年內啟動  2019年完成","createTime":"2017-11-23T05:28:51.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-24T01:46:29.000Z","uid":35790,"like":8,"dislike":69,"uniUserReply":56,"replies":[{"pid":"a0562ed094b0ff321e3bd01c6817cd97ba596b6a","tid":477460,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-23T05:28:51.000Z","msg":"《01》引消息：北京定23條立法時間表　明年內啟動　2019年完成<br />\n<br />\n立場報道<br />\n<br />\n2017/11/23 &mdash; 12:05<br />\n<br />\n網絡媒體《香港01》<br />\n<br />\n今天引述知情人士透露，北京已為23條立法制定框架時間表，而且來勢甚急，計劃最快在明年內便正式啟動，並在2019年完成，以免與2020年立法會選舉太接近，影響建制派選情。最大可能是明年9月或10月啟動，因《國歌法》及「一地兩檢」料已完成立法，「再無後顧之憂」。<br />\n<br />\n報道又引述消息人士稱，按北京強硬派的算盤，倘23條立法像03年般功敗垂成，最後的撒手鐧是，由人大常委會將國安法納入基本法附件三，變相立法，但也會等到立法會選舉後才出手，屆時距離林鄭月娥首屆特首任期完結仍有兩年，「時間相當鬆動」。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/01-%E5%BC%95%E6%B6%88%E6%81%AF-%E5%8C%97%E4%BA%AC%E5%AE%9A23%E6%A2%9D%E7%AB%8B%E6%B3%95%E6%99%82%E9%96%93%E8%A1%A8-%E6%98%8E%E5%B9%B4%E5%85%A7%E5%95%9F%E5%8B%95-2019%E5%B9%B4%E5%AE%8C%E6%88%90/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F01-%25E5%25BC%2595%25E6%25B6%2588%25E6%2581%25AF-%25E5%258C%2597%25E4%25BA%25AC%25E5%25AE%259A23%25E6%25A2%259D%25E7%25AB%258B%25E6%25B3%2595%25E6%2599%2582%25E9%2596%2593%25E8%25A1%25A8-%25E6%2598%258E%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E5%2585%25A7%25E5%2595%259F%25E5%258B%2595-2019%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E5%25AE%258C%25E6%2588%2590%2F&d=7Z0xoBeOu75rHjV%2FsWjGir%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=9b3e95b4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F01-%25E5%25BC%2595%25E6%25B6%2588%25E6%2581%25AF-%25E5%258C%2597%25E4%25BA%25AC%25E5%25AE%259A23%25E6%25A2%259D%25E7%25AB%258B%25E6%25B3%2595%25E6%2599%2582%25E9%2596%2593%25E8%25A1%25A8-%25E6%2598%258E%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E5%2585%25A7%25E5%2595%259F%25E5%258B%2595-2019%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E5%25AE%258C%25E6%2588%2590%2F&h=834b4b16\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/01-%E5%BC%95%E6%B6%88%